Google Play Services, AdMob, Log Data
Mobile Identifiers : When you are using our a mobile application that incorporates our Services, we may also automatically record your Google Advertising ID (if you are using an Android device), for advertising or analytics purposes. The Google Advertising ID is an anonymous identifier, provided by Google Play services. If your device has an Advertising ID, we may collect and use it for advertising and user analytics purposes. Please see below how you can reset you mobile Advertising ID or opt-out of receiving targeted ads through your mobile Advertising IDs.
